#. <section class="sutta" id="sn20.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn20.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 20"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 20"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Opammavagga"
msgstr "1. Similes"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 4. Okkhāsutta → okkhāsasuttaṃ (bj) | ukkhā (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn20.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Okkhāsutta"
msgstr "4. Rice Pots"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn20.4:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

#. VAR: okkhāsataṃ → ukkhāsataṃ (si, pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn20.4:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Yo, bhikkhave, pubbaṇhasamayaṃ okkhāsataṃ dānaṃ dadeyya, yo "
"majjhanhikasamayaṃ okkhāsataṃ dānaṃ dadeyya, yo sāyanhasamayaṃ okkhāsataṃ "
"dānaṃ dadeyya, yo vā pubbaṇhasamayaṃ antamaso gadduhanamattampi mettacittaṃ "
"bhāveyya, yo vā majjhanhikasamayaṃ antamaso gadduhanamattampi mettacittaṃ "
"bhāveyya, yo vā sāyanhasamayaṃ antamaso gadduhanamattampi mettacittaṃ "
"bhāveyya, idaṃ tato mahapphalataraṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, suppose one person was to give a gift of a hundred pots of rice "
"in the morning, at midday, and in the evening. And someone else was to "
"develop a heart of love, even just as long as it takes to pull a cow’s "
"udder. The latter would be more fruitful."

msgctxt "sn20.4:1.3"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "So you should train like this:"

msgctxt "sn20.4:1.4"
msgid ""
"‘mettā no cetovimutti bhāvitā bhavissati bahulīkatā yānīkatā vatthukatā "
"anuṭṭhitā paricitā susamāraddhā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘We will develop the heart’s release by love. We’ll cultivate it, make it "
"our vehicle and our basis, keep it up, consolidate it, and properly "
"implement it.’"

msgctxt "sn20.4:1.5"
msgid "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr "That’s how you should train.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn20.4:1.6"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
